snippet.title: Ultimate Summer - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
A mix of a third-person shooter and tower defense, you defend a ridiculously huge washing machine from demons by shooting them and setting traps and towers.

Ultimate Summer (C) Asmodev and Ultimate Games S.A.
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/664460/Ultimate_Summer/
